                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18350921-2048-offence-1 t18350921-cd-103"></join>5th Septem<lb></lb>ber</rs>. 1 plane, value 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18350921-name-783" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18350921-name-783" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350921-name-783" type="surname" value="HEIRON"></interp>
